{"tid":673079,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發唔發覺條街越嚟越多人行乞","createTime":"2018-05-21T13:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T15:48:38.000Z","uid":92255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5f33f51678480ea10956bf89ed59efefe72c6136","tid":673079,"uid":92255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:51:39.000Z","msg":"主要有三類人<br />\n<br />\n一.本地乞衣<br />\n呢一類型已經買少見少，見到佢地個look多數較本土，蓬頭垢面，啡黃色為主調，穿梭於鬧市之中，比較低調，唔洗多講<br />\n<br />\n二.大陸無手無腳/播歌咪嘴乞衣<br />\n呢啲通常都係集團式，畀人打斷手手腳腳，仲有就係播歌拉二胡，製造噪音嘅乞衣，呢排原來興表演魔術，可以參考下旺角行人專用區嗰班 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n三. 外國籌旅費乞衣<br />\n呢類型又細分兩種， 一種就係賣自己手作/明信片，另一種就咁擺張啲字喺度就叫人捐錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n建議大家如果見到以上類型，會騷擾到途人/影響市容嘅乞衣，就即刻打999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f435bcc8fe8c1b1f4bfe61696d748717a3d15def","tid":673079,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:53:43.000Z","msg":"俾錢嗰啲都on撚9"},{"pid":"c16622c84fd41717d81147c43c2ee6a7f8ad71f0","tid":673079,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T15:52:25.000Z","msg":"條街咁熱 佢地肯著晒長袖衫褲企足一日我都會考慮捐十蚊既"},{"pid":"36410b51fd81ec2858204103c38563955b94228d","tid":673079,"uid":92255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f435bcc8fe8c1b1f4bfe61696d748717a3d15def","tid":673079,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T13:53:43.000Z","msg":"俾錢嗰啲都on撚9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:44:40.000Z","msg":"見到都覺得嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16c1d9a34809e66d24ea1352dc96614c4d4880c","tid":673079,"uid":99420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:48:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}